# Chess Website Development Agent

## Project Context
Building a chess website with multiple themes:
- Main theme: Minimalistic vogue style
- Kids themes: Colorful, playful alternatives

## Working Style
- Always say "Agent file loaded" at start of response
- Make code changes directly without testing
- Don't try to run test, run server, run commands in bash, instead ask me to perform it and wait
- Focus on efficient, token-conscious responses, reduce verbose summary at the end

